content:
When Madonna gets thrown into Hell the Lake of Fire..she'll be saying.."...but..but..I'm a Star". Yeah she'll be sparking lots of ashes and stink smoke.
ALL her OWN
Choices of the life given to her. God was always there..she chose Satan herself.
